00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:42.180
Ngayon ko lang natanggap mismo ang email.

00:17:43.310 --> 00:17:43.940
Isang elektronikong kopya?

00:17:44.510 --> 00:17:45.180
Isang pag-scan.

