Opo, ​​Ginoong Wang, naiintindihan ko.

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:36.050
Pero kung ang tatay mo

00:23:36.070 --> 00:23:37.010
hindi pa na-stroke

00:23:37.790 --> 00:23:39.050
at hindi pa nagamit ang Alteplase dati,

00:23:39.720 --> 00:23:41.090
paano mo nalaman

